description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you interested in delivering patient centred care? We are looking for an experienced Critical Care Sister or Charge Nurse who is motivated and friendly who would like to work as part of our Critical Care Team. We are looking for a dynamic individual who is looking to take the next step in their leadership career. We are a friendly unit that strives to deliver high quality care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate must enjoy working as part of a Multi Disciplinary Team. We can provide you with excellent professional development opportunities led by our Clinical Educators who are passionate around developing the best critical care Nurses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The unit was rated as outstanding by the CQC and you will be joining at an exciting time as we are just undergoing a complete unit upgrade. As a Trust we endeavour to support flexible working requests which can be discussed at interview.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Senior Sister Linda Cross on 01423 554 597 or linda.cross12@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameLinda CrossJob titleSenior Sister/Unit ManagerEmail addresslinda.cross12@nhs.netTelephone number01423 554597&lt;/p&gt;
